Package: linecross
Title: Calculation of directional epistasis on linecross data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Geir H.", "Bolstad", email="geir.bolstad@nina.no", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Salom√©", "Bourg", email="salome.bourg@ntnu.no", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides tools for calculation directional epistasis on linecross data as defined in Hansen and Wagner (2001) <https://doi.org/10.1006/tpbi.2000.1508>. The package was released with in Bolstad et al. (2023), which contains detailed examples of use.
